---
title: Mexican Beef and Queso Fajitas with Tomato Salsa
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour. Sweet peppers and onions pair perfectly with tender beef for a fun fajita meal that all comes together with our fabulous, Mexican spice blend!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-and-queso-fajitas-f3cd30da.jpg
